{"tid":1324784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［7月7］［要片］［記者請進］山東街果3位義士，好需要你哋幫手","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T09:43:56.000Z","uid":54870,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1ee46e39b7ac47c40bb7132cc0438d5206b244","tid":1324784,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"一手（未經刪剪）嘅片段絕對可以幫到手，令佢哋有更大嘅機會打得甩<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋有片，麻煩send去民陣，民陣會轉交比有關人士<br />\n<br />\n亦都希望大家可以幫手推post，令更多人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468703-20190716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468703-20190716.htm&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=d2dfe2e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468703-20190716.htm&h=6a0c9128\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468703-20190716.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n3名反修例示威者涉非法禁錮及非禮　案件押後再訊<br />\n<br />\n九龍區反修例遊行期間，3名示威者要求一名女子刪除手機拍攝片段，涉嫌在爭執中撕扯女事主衣服及從後箍頸和胸部。警方以非法禁錮及非禮罪拘捕兩男一女，案件在九龍城裁判法院提堂，3名被告暫時毋須答辯。裁判官批准3名被告保釋，期間不得離開香港，亦不能直接或間接接觸證人。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，3名被告黃子隆、吳睿哲和蘇瑋善，在旺角山東街與西洋菜南街交界，涉非法囚禁事主，並對她造成不利。另外，黃子隆亦被控一項猥褻侵犯罪。女事主驗傷後發現前額、手臂和手腳有多處瘀傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方申請將案件押後至8月20日，以待警方進行科學鑑證，警方會繼續尋找目擊證人及在逃人士。"},{"pid":"cd824ac6c33699c24ddfa703b03a4b9ce12d850c","tid":1324784,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1866994dd76022b7c66415d4fa8e61f1fcdc6127","tid":1324784,"uid":111613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78d594b3d8b4fcf4f7fb3c8373015fe35cf5dd65","tid":1324784,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望佢地無事<br />\n黑警對暴力藍屍又唔見咁有效率"},{"pid":"28f3c4c626b7d6985aa31c732f16d6faf63e00cf","tid":1324784,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我冇嘢講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4125578e43ecfef1eb430074979b7bf362052792","tid":1324784,"uid":11929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c421ddaa110248e6855cc83f4e2042437a3f8422","tid":1324784,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c557a9d41f88eb15c6e1d1d82bb26246dafd10c6","tid":1324784,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你，用外國勢力救救前線！<br />\n<br />\n  <span style=\"color: red;\">[我都要攬炒]一齊上twitter將黑警權力過大揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊！！！ </span><br />\n<br />\n文字template係#72！！！照copy就得！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1324656/page/1！！\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1324656/page/1！！</a>"},{"pid":"f81a9282a82a0f60c0aab7c99d8c23149c07b493","tid":1324784,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n有冇巴打絲打有方法搵到錄影，又或者在場知道女商人被誤認女警的過程？ <br />\n好需要大家幫忙 <br />\n請幫手推"},{"pid":"df7e9a10527553df160558bceed422ca42335a29","tid":1324784,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n有冇巴打絲打有方法搵到錄影，又或者在場知道女商人被誤認女警的過程？ <br />\n好需要大家幫忙 <br />\n請幫手推"},{"pid":"a40624297996f4e0a06cbb1d83bce8a012e84b1c","tid":1324784,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n有冇巴打絲打有方法搵到錄影，又或者在場知道女商人被誤認女警的過程？ <br />\n好需要大家幫忙 <br />\n請幫手推"},{"pid":"68087eee601b779143dfeb499979ed79491ac94f","tid":1324784,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:28:11